=== COVID-19期間指控政敵及違反政府防疫指示 ===
於[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]期間，洪錦鉉於社交媒體聲稱7月15日晚已「傳出」有[[寶達邨|寶達邨]]居民確診的消息，指控政敵馮家龍未及時作出反應，但[[衞生署_(香港)|衞生署]]只在7月16日才公佈寶達邨有居民確診<ref name="#1"/>。另外，洪亦被揭發，在7月有多人確診的「藍絲雅蘭迎囍聚會」擔任主禮嘉賓，更除罩與人合照，又帶領眾人大合唱<ref>{{Cite web|title=雅蘭迎囍聚會群組多人確診 無戴口罩合照言談甚歡|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%85%E8%98%AD%E8%BF%8E%E5%9B%8D%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%84%A1%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%90%88%E7%85%A7%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%87%E7%94%9A%E6%AD%A1-113916620.html|accessdate=2021-04-23|work=hk.news.yahoo.com|language=zh-Hant-HK|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430092453/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%9B%85%E8%98%AD%E8%BF%8E%E5%9B%8D%E8%81%9A%E6%9C%83%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E7%84%A1%E6%88%B4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%90%88%E7%85%A7%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%87%E7%94%9A%E6%AD%A1-113916620.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=雅蘭迎囍聚會群組多人確診 無戴口罩合照言談甚歡|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200718/bkn-20200718193916595-0718_00822_001.html|accessdate=2021-04-23|work=on.cc東網|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423054104/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200718/bkn-20200718193916595-0718_00822_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

